{"about_the_game":"<br>Join the official <strong>Discord server</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ROGUE MACHINES HAVE INVADED</h2>An army of intelligent machines have gone rogue in post-war cities. Your highly skilled 3-man team has been commissioned to pilot the <i>Falconet</i>, an advanced weapons entity, to rescue the humans trapped behind enemy lines. <br><br>On your team you have Bangs the engineer, Spike the navigator, and Flo the pilot of the <i>Falconet</i>. You will need to shoot your way through each retro style level to eliminate enemies\u2026 before they eliminate you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">USE WEAPONS IN COMBOS</h2>Rapidly switch between your diverse arsenal of weapons with unlimited ammo to annihilate enemies in satisfying combos.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803070/extras/Guns_variety_2.gif?t=1730797227\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PROGRESS BY SOLVING PUZZLES</h2>Gain access to restricted areas in each level using the <i>Falconet\u2019s</i> 6 different colour-coded weapons and your problem-solving skills to take out enemies and generators.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803070/extras/Door_generator_gif.gif?t=1730797227\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">RESCUE HUMAN SURVIVORS</h2>Search out survivors in captured areas and bring back hope to the humans you liberate.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803070/extras/Rescue_humans_gif.gif?t=1730797227\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">RACK UP HIGH SCORES</h2>Beat the records you set as you improve in your gun-wielding skills.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803070/extras/gif7.gif?t=1730797227\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803070/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730797227","background_raw":"https://shar